# Test artifacts generated by render/number/staleness tests that run
# directly against the fixture directory (audit smoke test, staleness
# smoke test). The `.dot.reference` files ARE checked in as the
# byte-identity anchor for Task 5's render test; everything else is
# regenerated per-run and should not pollute the fixture.
doc/figures/dags/*-auto.dot
doc/figures/dags/*-auto.png
doc/figures/dags/*-numbered.dot
doc/figures/dags/*-numbered.png
# Audit log written by `dag audit --fix` when unpropagated tasks exist.
doc/figures/dags/.audit-unpropagated-*.md
